      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_61DB2DC0-E0DB-0138-3FE0-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Inbox</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="select_conversation" data-step-uuid="61DB40D0-E0DB-0138-3FE1-12F2183ABDFB">
    <h2 id="select_conversation" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Conversation</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/637/918/original/325f5b7b-adfd-4b8b-9c47-926865f87b65.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/637/918/medium/325f5b7b-adfd-4b8b-9c47-926865f87b65.png" srcset="" alt="Select Conversation" height="387" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_61DB66D0-E0DB-0138-3FE3-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the conversation you want to respond to [1]. Click the <strong>Reply</strong> icon in the message header, or hover over the timestamp and click the <strong>Reply</strong> icon within the message [2]. You can also click the <strong>Reply</strong> icon in the toolbar [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="reply_to_message" data-step-uuid="61DB7B20-E0DB-0138-3FE4-12F2183ABDFB">
    <h2 id="reply_to_message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Reply to Message</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/637/920/original/cbd055eb-9e08-4201-948b-5fcb4c9dee48.png" srcset="" alt="Reply to Message" height="679" width="758">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_61DB9FD0-E0DB-0138-3FE6-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Type your reply in the message field [1]. You can attach a file or media [2]. When you are ready, click the <strong>Send </strong>button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_sent_message" data-step-uuid="61DBB2B0-E0DB-0138-3FE7-12F2183ABDFB">
